window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>When DJ and the team get a mission to a dangerous part of the world, there is suspicion their new employer is not telling them the whole truth. Things become much harder than they were promised. Still, they pull off the job with the skills and cunning we have come to expect from Slaughter and crew.</p> <p>When things are over is when the trouble truly begins.</p> <p>What is the secret behind this sudden betrayal?</p> <p>The path to uncovering the truth becomes a journey into the past, and the team suffers greatly along the way.</p> <p>You will love this sixth book because it will keep you racing to the end.</p>"; 
